data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
Age Restrictions: Patrons under 13 years old must be accompanied by an adult. Certain games or content may have specific age restrictions, and proof of age may be required.
Respectful behavior towards other patrons and staff is mandatory. Harassment, bullying, or disruptive behavior will not be tolerated.
Outside Food and Drinks: No outside food or beverages are allowed unless otherwise specified by management or Authorized of the Owner.
Refunds: Refunds for unused gaming time or purchases will be provided only under specific conditions, such as equipment failure not caused by the patron.
